   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <head>19.5.1884 Montag</head>
            <p>
               <placeName type="write" key="49069">Hamburg</placeName> May 19. 1884.</p>
            <p>
               <persName key="1314">Nenne</persName> and <persName key="1153">Belle
                  Hasperg</persName> came at about four today and asked me to dinner. So I started
               at 5 o&#x2019;clock. It was thundering and lightning a great deal. <persName key="1316">Puppe</persName> and <persName key="1317">his wife</persName> dined there with
               me. <persName key="1609">Alice</persName> was invited too but was of course left
               behind as she always is, whenever there is any inventable reason for doing so. Today
               it was on account of the thunderstorm. After dinner we drove away in the dog cart,
                  <persName key="1314">Nenne</persName> driving, and <persName key="1153">Belle</persName> sitting next to her, I and <persName key="72975">Heine</persName> at the back. We drove right round the Alster. As we were getting
               near home the spring broke so that we were almost jolted out of our skins as we
               bumped over the stones. Soon the cover for our feet fell out too, so we had to get
               out and stop to get it. At last after many vicissitades we managed to get home.</p>
         </div>
